###################
# Documentation Strategy
###################

# Documentation (local only - use DOCUMENTATION_MAP.md to find files)
# Strategy: Track only essential docs, keep development docs local
*.md

# Essential documentation (tracked)
!DOCUMENTATION_MAP.md
!README.md
!docs/SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE_OVERVIEW.md
!docs/design/EVENTS_SERVICE_MVP.md
!docs/design/ELECTIONS_SERVICE_MVP.md
!docs/status/CURRENT_PRODUCTION_STATUS.md
!docs/status/SECURITY_HARDENING_PLAN.md
!docs/guides/SECRET_MANAGER.md
!docs/security/CLOUDFLARE_SETUP.md
!docs/security/CLOUDFLARE_AUTOMATION.md
!members/README.md

# GitHub templates (tracked)
!.github/
!.github/**/*.md
!.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/*.md

###################
# Scripts & Tools
###################

# Shell scripts (local only - available on request)
*.sh
!.github/workflows/*.sh
!scripts/*.sh

# Python validation (tracked - needed for CI)
# validate_documentation_map.py is tracked

